version.changelog:
Added SelectLTBVCAudioSources.lua
Besides some minor bug fixes this release contains the following new script:
- SelectLTBVCAudioSources.lua: allows the simple selection of the audio source for each voice by a selection dialog in a Reaper project conforming to LTBVC conventions (for example, to compare the rendering of the MIDI or raw audio file with the refined audio file in the final mix)}
